==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ossianic
<hw>Os`si*an"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to, or characteristic of,
<persfn><etsep>Ossian</etsep></persfn>, a legendary Erse or Celtic
bard.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The compositions might be fairly classed as
<qex>Ossianic</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>G. Eliot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ossicle</ent>⟦br⟧
